name: Manpages.alfredworkflow
body:
# Alfred 2 workflow for Manpages
**[Download!](https://github.com/skyzyx/manpages.alfredworkflow/raw/master/manpages.alfredworkflow)** Requires [Alfred 2 and the Powerpack](http://www.alfredapp.com/powerpack/). Updates can be found and installed using **[Alleyoop](http://alfred.daniel.sh/Workflows/Alleyoop.alfredworkflow)**.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
